---
description: Extra safety for category/product clone tasks in the shop
alwaysApply: true
---
For shop clone tasks:
- Category pages live at `shop/<category-slug>/index.html`
- Product pages live at `shop/<category-slug>/<product-slug>/index.html`
- Product data is generated by `shop/scan_shop.py` into `shop/data/shop-catalog.json`
- Category images live at `shop/media/<category-slug>.*`
- Product cover image is `media/main.*`; all remaining images become gallery images

Before finishing a clone-related edit, verify:
- current slug comes from folder/URL/data, not an old hardcoded value
- product route and category route are correct
- page text does not still describe the old cloned item
- media fallback does not pull from the old category/product
